</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><note place="topright"><ab facs="#facs_492_line_1592199151432_768">gleytſbrıef </ab>
</note><ab facs="#facs_492_r1l3"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> wır <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mıt <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleıſʒ / daʒ eẅr gnade <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_492_r1l4"><expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> vnd kawffleẅt vnd auch Jr hab vnd <expan>kawffmanſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> vnd dıe Jren </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_492_r1l5">in dıe <expan>nehſtkünftıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>frankfurt<ex>er</ex></expan> herbſtmeſſe vnd <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> darawſʒ mıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_492_r1l6">geleyt <expan>gnedıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> fürſehen welle . Alſo ob ſıe <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıe Jren ʒu <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_492_r1l7"><expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> oder <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> den <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd des begern / daʒ denn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_492_r1l8">ſıe vnd das Jr durch <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> lande <expan>h<ex>e</ex>rſchaft</expan> vnd gepıet ſıcher </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_492_r1l9">geleytet <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> . als etc . das wellen etc / Vnd bıtten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_492_r1l10">des eẅr gnedıg <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> antwurt <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> bey dıſem <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> dıener </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_492_r1l11"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>ſab<ex>at</ex>o</expan> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Lorencij </ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter"><ab facs="#facs_492_r1l12"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> <expan>Ercʒbıſch<ex>of</ex></expan> ʒu Maincʒ </ab>
