<ab facs="#facs_492_r1l17"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ʒu Pıkembach vnd <expan>Burggraf<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>Mıltemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_492_r1l18"><expan>Dıeth<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>lantſchad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>vıcʒtu<ex>m</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>Aſchaffemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_492_r1l19"><expan>mutat<ex>is</ex></expan> <expan>muta<ex>n</ex>dıs</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_492" id="245r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Bischof von Wirczburg</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><app><note place="above">Gleytsbrief</note></app><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, wir <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr
                                <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mit
                            <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz, daz ewr gnade
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und kawfflewt und auch ir hab und
                                <expan>kawffmans<ex>chaft</ex></expan> und die iren in die
                                <expan>nehstkünftig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Frankfurt<ex>er</ex></expan> herbstmesse und
                            <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> darawsz mit geleyt
                                <expan>gnedikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> fürsehen welle, also ob sie
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> die iren zu
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> oder <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> den
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> und des begern, daz denn sie und das ir durch
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> lande, <expan>h<ex>e</ex>rschaft</expan> und
                        gepiet sicher geleytet <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, als etc. Das wellen
                        etc. Und bitten des ewr gnedig <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> antwurt
                                <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> bey disem
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> diener. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Lorencii.</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>, <expan>erczbisch<ex>of</ex></expan> zu
                        Maincz<lb/>Graf <expan>Johanns<ex>en</ex></expan> von
                                Wertheim<lb/><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Lienhart<ex>en</ex></expan>, grafen und
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> zu
                            Castell<lb/><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> Schenken, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> zu
                                Lyntpurg<lb/><expan>Arnold<ex>en</ex></expan> von Sekendorff,
                                <expan>amptm<ex>an</ex></expan> zu der
                                Newenstat,<lb/><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> zu Pikembach
                        und <expan>burggraf<ex>en</ex></expan> zu
                                <expan>Miltemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan><lb/><expan>Dieth<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Lantschad<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>vicztu<ex>m</ex></expan> zu
                                <expan>Aschaffemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
<expan>mutat<ex>is</ex></expan>
<expan>muta<ex>n</ex>dis</expan>
</ab>
